Description:
Trendy Lifestyle or Great Investment!
Within walking distance to shops, schools and recreation facilities 2 Jade Walk presents as the perfect beginning for a first home buyer, investor or an able residence for the downsizer. This Officer townhouse has been immaculately maintained nestled in the leafy surrounds of Officer it will tick all the boxes, offering you:
- Three bedrooms, master with walk-in robe and en-suite;
- Open plan living and dining room;
- Split-system cooling and ducted heating;
- Modern kitchen with all appliances you'd expect to find in a new house;
- Double car remote garage;
- Ample size yard;
This home is ideal for those looking to invest in a fast growing area and not expected to last!
